{
  "stem": "19895.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And communications with Sweden are not necessarily the best.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And who are the Lichtmanns to find out and so forth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we tried to contact Red Cross and so on, and tell it to them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a week went by, and we were just living on hope.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And another 10 days went by, or a week went by, and we were living on the hope that somebody will answer and so on.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And father gave our address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't live in the same location as at that time, and so forth, which is too long to go into on how it worked.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a person who lived in the same building where I lived until I was about from age 9-- age 8, age 9, until around age 14, when we had to leave it, because Jews were not permitted to continue in that job where my father and mother was to be an attendant in an apartment building.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a shoemaker, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Molina.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I spent an awful lot of time with Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Molina because, as a child, I admired looking at as he was sitting on his little stool, and in his lap and his apron, he had the shoes which he either fixed or made a new, shoe and had all these wooden pegs in his mouth, and so expertly was spitting them out, one after the other, and hammering them in, and making the shoes.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he always had to sit there doing his work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was always kind to talk to me when I was looking for somebody to talk to as a little boy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
